data.description: A MUST SEE newly renovated Downtown condo, used as second home that is barely lived in! All new appliances, furniture, rugs, and televisions will be included with a full purchase price. One-minute walk to Miami Dade College (Downtown campus), three-minute walk to the famous Bayside Market and Miami Heat games, five-minute drive to Miami Port Authority (Cruise Line Terminals) and a ten-minute drive to both Miami International Airport and South Beach (Ocean Drive). This condo centralized location is a Hipsters’ paradise as it offers immediate access to all the great Downtown and Brickell restaurants, coffee shops, bars, and endless shopping. The building authorizes both long and short-term leases. The condo comes with one discounted ($60 per month) designated parking spot
